{"tid":1834900,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"《蘋果》直擊麥理浩夫人度假村 職員：收到通知指營地「要候命」","createTime":"2020-01-22T15:11:07.000Z","updateTime":"2020-01-23T04:01:27.000Z","uid":212626,"like":13,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":14,"replies":[{"pid":"2146f198085e4ce2f8f3a4a8572437da8dadb6c7","tid":1834900,"uid":212626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-22T15:11:07.000Z","msg":"來自武漢的新型冠狀病毒蔓延至不同地方，香港亦在今日確診首宗武漢肺炎，食物及衞生局局長陳肇始早前指康文署初步已預留兩個度假營，以便隔離與患者有緊密接觸人士。<span style=\"color: red;\">據知，麥理浩夫人度假村已安排營地內的人士離開，預計最少被徵用14日</span>。《蘋果》今午到麥理浩夫人度假村視察，發現度假村內僅有3至4名職員工作，全部人都有戴口罩，但營地內則未見任何市民，烏燈黑火，場面冷清。<span style=\"color: red;\">有職員向記者透露，他們今日收到通知指營地「要候命」，外來人不能進入營地內</span>，但營地內則未有任何防疫措施準備，亦未知衞生署人員是否有到營地協助「收場」。<br />\n<br />\n麥理浩夫人度假營以獨立式平房為主，每間供3至15人使用，整個營最多容納268人，資料顯示今、明兩日均有近百人留宿，年三十至年初三關閉，之後重開，每日均有人報名參加日營或宿營。<br />\n<br />\n2003年3月31日，政府因應淘大花園E座爆發「沙士」疫情，衞生署署長發出隔離令，要求E座住戶共約300人，即晚遷入鯉魚門公園度假營及麥理浩夫人度假村。由於消息公佈倉卒，不少住戶也是從新聞報道得知要離開淘大花園，漏夜被穿着整套保護裝備的人員帶到兩個偏遠營地，近兩個月後才回家。在營地內，醫護人員會為隔離者派發抗病毒藥物利巴韋林，及定期檢查他們身體狀況。個別被隔離者曾表示，當時營內沒有通訊設備，無法得悉外界情況；營內要共用廁所、房間之間的天花互通，感覺不佳；有人因為不安而需尋求心理輔導。<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/breaking/20200122/Y4OSQUX6MSVEBHHEZRQTZ6I2FI/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Fbreaking%2F20200122%2FY4OSQUX6MSVEBHHEZRQTZ6I2FI%2F&d=UWp4lduD54HchuVgBglmzb32HZRMtn4xjJY4gFhUisg%3D&h=5fb681d1\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Fbreaking%2F20200122%2FY4OSQUX6MSVEBHHEZRQTZ6I2FI%2F&h=75e78256\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/breaking/20200122/Y4OSQUX6MSVEBHHEZRQTZ6I2FI/</a>"},{"pid":"d5722728612f837cbb587e4028b50a2a6c0d63ce","tid":1834900,"uid":76310,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-22T15:11:49.000Z","msg":"要求香港真雙普選作為第二階段中美貿易協議一部份<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://petitions.whitehouse.gov/petition/appeal-add-genuine-dual-universal-suffrage-hong-kong-part-phase-2-agreement-between-us-and-china\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fpetitions.whitehouse.gov%2Fpetition%2Fappeal-add-genuine-dual-universal-suffrage-hong-kong-part-phase-2-agreement-between-us-and-china&d=UWp4lduD54HchuVgBglmzb32HZRMtn4xjJY4gFhUisg%3D&h=33ae82c9\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://petitions.whitehouse.gov/petition/appeal-add-genuine-dual-universal-suffrage-hong-kong-part-phase-2-agreement-between-us-and-china</a><br />\n要求香港真雙普選作為第二階段中美貿易協議一部份<br />\n<br />\n而家美帝要求強国簽左第二階段先撤關稅<br />\n所以強国一定要被迫情況下同美帝簽協議<br />\n香港要搭順風車<br />\n<br />\n另外, 所羅門聯署:<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://petitions.whitehouse.gov/petition/beijing-2022-winter-olympics-corporate-sponsors-dont-deserve-tax-benefits-so-dont-help-them-fund-ccp-propaganda-again\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fpetitions.whitehouse.gov%2Fpetition%2Fbeijing-2022-winter-olympics-corporate-sponsors-dont-deserve-tax-benefits-so-dont-help-them-fund-ccp-propaganda-again&d=UWp4lduD54HchuVgBglmzb32HZRMtn4xjJY4gFhUisg%3D&h=e2afb1f4\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://petitions.whitehouse.gov/petition/beijing-2022-winter-olympics-corporate-sponsors-dont-deserve-tax-benefits-so-dont-help-them-fund-ccp-propaganda-again</a><br />\n0<br />\n0"},{"pid":"464dd5dbdd0f69820c9436d526ea03bb0df1f51d","tid":1834900,"uid":20262,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-22T15:12:41.000Z","msg":"集中營<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ed0882623e160b595356b57c17c82d81835f9c22","tid":1834900,"uid":156913,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-22T15:13:45.000Z","msg":"入咗去如果犯法會點?<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9dfb3f70bd3873d303e7cfadb854980ff2e31f12","tid":1834900,"uid":79410,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-01-22T15:14:03.000Z","msg":"叫L 晒班藍絲去守啦, 仆街"},{"pid":"d29116bad0d794b22a22eacf61d8c6a37a0fd123","tid":1834900,"uid":63154,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-